    {
      "reviewId": "places/ChIJm9zzJnW3yhQRHmF9bN2hrZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCT05XWjVTRXBIVERacWJqbExWREkyWkVJME5sRRAB",
      "text": "Emirhan was helping us and kindly serving us. He truly is always around at the breakfast & lunch area. He even brought me a fruit platter with all the seasonal fruits & i loved it. Overall, Food 10/10, atmosphere 10/10 and Emirhan 10/10 for sure!!!\n\nI stayed in room 711 and oh my god the room was always clean, i mean always. I’d go have my breakfast at 9 am and when i come back at 10-10:30 am, i’d find this amazing house keeping Fehmiye organising it and cleaning it. I mean i keep important things in there and not once did i not trust this amazing lady Fehmiye. She’s so sweet, so clean and the rooms always smell great & amazing thanks to this beautiful soul in & out Fehmiye.",
