    {
      "reviewId": "places/ChIJm9zzJnW3yhQRHmF9bN2hrZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sWE5WRkhVM05RUkdwa2JGbExWVFJLVmsxa1lVRRAB",
      "text": "I sincerely adored my stay and was genuinely disappointed to leave so soon. I truly wished I could have stayed longer. The room was impeccable, the cleanliness outstanding, and the service consistently excellent despite the hotel being fully packed and hosting VIP events. Even the marketing team, Zeineb and Ipek, embody a rare and exceptional attitude: “no problem we can’t solve, and we’ll go to any length to make you happy.” This is the true ethos of hospitality and exactly why guests choose one hotel over another, even within the same brand and group.\n\nTheir generosity shines through in every detail. The lady concierge managed to find things even ChatGPT couldn’t track down, which speaks volumes about her resourcefulness. As for the wonderful hostess manager, Lauretta, she makes you feel instantly at home, as if you were an old friend stopping by for a visit.\n\nAll of this reflects the strength of the general manager Utkan Gulacti leading the property.\n\nIn my opinion, a hotel represents not only its brand but also the team that brings it to life, and here, the entire team feels like a group of true stars. They deserve sincere applause. I wholeheartedly commend them for their attention to details, their quick response despite being extremely busy,  please keep  up the good work, and honestly, my next stay can only be in this hotel. They made leaving incredibly difficult and left me wishing I had spent my entire time there. I hope to see them soon.",
